27	# Split widget: {{widgetName}}
28	
29	Extract the `{{widgetName}}` widget subtree from `{{screenPath}}` into its own file at `{{widgetFile}}`.
30	
31	## Steps
32	
33	1. **Read** — Load `{{screenPath}}`.
34	2. **Locate** — Find the widget subtree implementing `{{widgetName}}`. Use the description in `.stitch/designs/{{screenId}}/widgets.jsonl` (the entry with `name == "{{widgetName}}"`) to disambiguate.
